sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" data-src=\"/now2/assets/static/serverless.42db587.7868748e6d794e39c449dcedc91deca6.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/now2/assets/static/serverless.42db587.7868748e6d794e39c449dcedc91deca6.png\" width=\"2560\"></noscript></p>\n<p>Software is eating the world. Unfortunately, most businesses still can't deliver software successfully, and very few do so at the pace needed to stay competitive. For those who wish to keep up, let alone lead, software delivery &#x26; operation must be radically simplified.</p>\n<h2 id=\"open-source-solution-serverless\"><a href=\"#open-source-solution-serverless\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Open Source Solution: Serverless</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.serverless.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Serverless</a> is built on next-generation public cloud services that auto-scale and charge only when used. When scale, capacity planning &#x26; cost management are automated, the result is software that's easier to build, maintain, and often up-to 99% cheaper.</p>\n<p>But, Serverless Architectures are new and therefore require a shift in how we previously thought about architectures &#x26; workflows. The goal at Serverless Inc. is to give developers, teams and orgs all of the tools they need to build and operate serverless applications in one simple, powerful &#x26; elegant experience.</p>\n<h2 id=\"why-use-serverless\"><a href=\"#why-use-serverless\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Why use Serverless?</h2>\n<p>Coming ...</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-is-it-related-to-our-grid\"><a href=\"#how-is-it-related-to-our-grid\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>How is it related to our grid?</h2>\n<p>Coming ...</p>\n<h2 id=\"serverless-apps-that-can-run-on-the-grid\"><a href=\"#serverless-apps-that-can-run-on-the-grid\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Serverless Apps that can run on the grid</h2>\n<p>Coming ...</p>\n","sidebar":"docs","next":"/docs/gridsome/","prev":"/docs/zeroci/","headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"Serverless App Framework","anchor":"#serverless-app-framework"},{"depth":2,"value":"Open Source Solution: Serverless","anchor":"#open-source-solution-serverless"},{"depth":2,"value":"Why use Serverless?","anchor":"#why-use-serverless"},{"depth":2,"value":"How is it related to our grid?","anchor":"#how-is-it-related-to-our-grid"},{"depth":2,"value":"Serverless Apps that can run on the grid","anchor":"#serverless-apps-that-can-run-on-the-grid"}]},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/docs/zeroci/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/wiki-publisher/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/wiki-publisher/","title":"Wiki Publisher"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/virtual-spaces/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/video-sharing/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/video-conf/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/tomochain/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/tfgrid/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/serverless/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/publishing-tool/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/upcoming-projects/","title":"Coming Up!"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/index/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/why-threefold-now/","title":"Why ThreeFold Now?"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/harmony/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/gridsome/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/gitea/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/dmcustomers/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/dmcollab/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/dmcircles/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/digitalme/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/digibyte/img/readme/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/decentralized-office-intro/img/readme/","title